ICDCS CALL FOR PAPERS , May 31 - June 4 , 1999
Today , the ubquitous World Wide Web provides abundant opportunities and paradigms for various kinds of applications . The ICDCS Web Application Workshop is to provide an international forum for scientists , engineers , computer users , and students to exchange and share their experences , new ideas , and research results about the state-of-the-art research , development , and implementations of web-based systems , technologies , and applications . Topics of interests include , but are not limited to : Web accessibility Interoperability Scalability Interactive databases Web-based Visualization Search engines Mobile agents Distributed object technology Multimedia support Resource management
WORKSHOP PAPER SUBMISSION :
Please submit three hard copies of papers ( not exceeding 8 double space pages , including your email address ) to the Workshop Program Chair , no later than Oct . 7 , 1998 : Professor Wei Sun Chair , ICDCS Web- Based Application Workshop School of Computer Science Florida International University Miami , FL 33199 Email : weisun @ fiu . edu Tel : ( 305 ) 348 - 3751 Fax : ( 305 ) 248 - 3549 All papers are to be reviewed . Accepted Workshop papers will be presented at the Workshop and will be published in the ICDCS Proceedings as short papers . For ICDCS paper submission , please submit directly to ICDCS .
